							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="dev-block">
							<div class="block-text">
								<p class="block-name">2D Heat Diffusion</p>
								<p class="block-desc">
									Simulates heat transfer by conduction through a two dimensional plate. Computationally solves the heat
									partial differential equation and visualizes the solution as a heatmap.
								</p>
								<div class="block-ingredients">
									<enhanced:img src="../../assets/matlab.png" alt="Matlab Icon"/>
								</div>
							</div>
							<a class="block-pic" href="{githubRepo}/2d-heat-diffusion" target="_blank">
								<enhanced:img src="../../assets/proj2.png" alt="Matlab Project"/>
							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="dev-block">
							<div class="block-text">
								<p class="block-name">The Lair</p>
								<p class="block-desc">A fictional online storefront set in a world populated by vampires.</p>
								<div class="block-ingredients">
									<enhanced:img src="../../assets/javascript.png" alt="Javascript Icon" />
									<enhanced:img src="../../assets/react.png" alt="React Icon" />
								</div>
							</div>
							<a class="block-pic" href="{githubRepo}/shopping-cart" target="_blank">
								<enhanced:img src="../../assets/proj3.png" alt="Storefront Project" />
							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="dev-block">
							<div class="block-text">
								<p class="block-name">CV Maker</p>
								<p class="block-desc">A simple CV maker that allows users to customize and download their CV.</p>
								<div class="block-ingredients">
									<enhanced:img src="../../assets/javascript.png" alt="Javascript Icon" />
									<enhanced:img src="../../assets/react.png" alt="React Icon" />
								</div>
							</div>
							<a class="block-pic" href="{githubRepo}/cv-project" target="_blank">
								<enhanced:img src="../../assets/proj4.png" alt="CV Maker Project" />
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="divider menu-divider dev-body-block"></div>
			<Anchor id="contact" />
			<Form/>
			<div class="body-art dev-body-block">
				<div class="body-container">
					<button
						class="switch-body"
						>
						SWITCH TO <br /> DAYTIME
						<enhanced:img src="../../assets/dev_pp.png" alt="developer profile" class="profile-pic" />
